eproduction instructions.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.svg?3224b641ed840fa2\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" sizes=\"any\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><a href=\"#content\" class=\"skip-link\">Skip to content</a><header class=\"site-header\"><a class=\"wordmark\" aria-label=\"Vela home\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"wordmark-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">V</span><span>VELA</span></a><nav aria-label=\"Primary\"><a href=\"/frontiers\">Frontiers</a><a href=\"/docs\">Docs</a><a href=\"/search\">Search</a></nav><span class=\"release-chip\">site 0.200</span></header><main id=\"content\"><section class=\"hero\"><div class=\"hero-copy\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Scientific state, without the theatre</p><h1>See what is known, what is merely verified, and what still needs a human decision.</h1><p class=\"lede\">Vela preserves immutable research history and exposes exact roots. Agents may produce and verify evidence. They do not accept scientific claims.</p><div class=\"hero-actions\"><a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"/frontiers\">Browse frontiers</a><a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"/docs\">How the boundary works</a></div></div><div class=\"hero-ledger\" aria-label=\"Published state summary\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Published snapshot</p><div class=\"hero-metrics\"><div class=\"metric\"><strong>4</strong><span>frontiers</span></div><div class=\"metric\"><strong>2,829</strong><span>findings</span></div><div class=\"metric\"><strong>2,327</strong><span>events</span></div></div><div class=\"hero-root\"><span>Erdős event root</span><code title=\"sha256:6695ff579abba6dfbeb1e20d3a40e3975257b5a322e4b18f8746839dc93780b2\">sha256:6695ff579abba6dfbeb1e20d…</code></div></div></section><section class=\"decision-strip\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Human authority boundary</p><h2>Decision awaiting a human</h2></div><div class=\"decision-body\"><div class=\"decision-state\"><span class=\"sta